# Agentic Workflow Governance — .gitignore
# Documentation/specification repository (Markdown).
# No language-specific build artifacts to ignore yet — entries below cover
# OS cruft, editor caches, and common temp/backup files only.

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- Editor / IDE caches ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project

# --- Temp / backup files ---
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*~
